text: Jorge Sánchez García (8 April, 1943) is a Mexican worker and politician. He was a member of the Institutional Revolutionary Party. Sánchez was born in Tequixquiac, Mexico. He was leader from Sindicato Mexicano de Eléctristas. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Politicians from Mexico (state) Category:Politicians from Mexico City Category:Mexican activists Category:People from Tequixquiac Category:Mexican people of Spanish descent
